text: Rómulo Bouzas Rodríguez is a retired rower from Mexico. Rodríguez competed at the 2000 Summer Olympics. He was born on 28 February 1978.Rómulo Bouzas == References == Category:1978 births Category:Living people Category:Mexican rowers Category:Olympians for Mexico Category:Sportspeople from Mexico City
